	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Load up GustavDev/BGO_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- goto 8 43 223&#xD;&#xA;- Step forward into Wyrm's Rock fortress - approach the two flaming fists in front:&#xD;&#xA;S_WYR_Fortress_FlamingFist001_40893ed8-ef6c-437f-9ef3-3fa2c7ac3a98&#xD;&#xA;S_WYR_Fortress_FlamingFist002_baaf58e1-8880-4dda-a351-4d4680c3cb2f&#xD;&#xA;- If a brainquake happens, they will do the AD after it is finished" />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="4" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Vignette AD for the Flaming Fist in the entrance hall of Wyrm's Rock in Wyrm's Crossing.&#xD;&#xA;Vignette summary:&#xD;&#xA;&quot;People are going back and forth on an hourly basis usually. We should still see traces of Flaming Fists coming and going, as well as show the omnipresence of the Steel Watchers and other security systems (inert traps from Gortash’s boss fight that activate only if you attack him at the ceremony would be great).&quot;" />
